Content:
Biggest crashes brought us down 93% and 86%. Right now we held in the middle of nowhere at 82%. People might take out some money after new year to pay taxes and dec/jan has often weak price action / low volume. 1170 is a 94% drop from ATH to old ATH. I expect resistance at the 200weekly MA and strong resistance at previous resistance of old ATH.
